Rolfe Sedan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rolfe_Sedan 0 Rolfe Sedan (January 20, 1896 – September 15, 1982) was an American character actor, best known for appearing in bit parts, often uncredited, usually portraying clerks, train conductors, postmen, cooks, waiters etc. Rolfe_Sedan ( January_20_,_1896 – September_15_,_1982 ) was an_American_character_actor , best_known for appearing in bit_parts , often uncredited , usually portraying clerks , train_conductors , postmen , cooks , waiters etc .
